('20b64055-25ea-4008-a58e-9ea56b7f39d0', 'illiquid-exit-trading-launch-launchdayv-0', 'trading', 'Illiquid exit (trading)', 'You need out of a thinly traded name, but your own selling moves the price. Dumping fast eats slippage; scaling out risks the news breaking first. The clock is running.'),
('ed314526-b17f-4dd2-bf47-84ad1ee7a6ab', 'rate-decision-surprise-trading-launch-launchdayv-1', 'trading', 'Rate decision surprise (trading)', 'The central bank just did the opposite of what the market priced in. Every model in front of you is instantly stale, and the tape is moving faster than you can think. Everyone is watching how you handle it.'),
('83a8e489-8986-4050-8197-507a8aed9c75', 'drawdown-streak-trading-launch-launchdayv-2', 'trading', 'Drawdown streak (trading)', 'Six losing trades in a row. The system says keep sizing normally; every instinct says shrink, sit out, or double up to win it back.'),
